book that puts a lot into perspective she said it goes 
directly from my heart to the page 
blanchard is unopposed in michigans aug 7 primary while 
engler is expected to easily defeat tax fighter john lauve a march 
poll found blanchard leading engler 51 percent to 31 percent but 
the lesserknown engler said that was to be expected early in the 
campaign 
