the boot camp ad tight budgets ahead and 78yearold lt gov 
martha griffiths decision not to retire which came as a surprise 
to the governor 
the carefully constructed facade is in tatters engler said 
this is a very isolated administration that isnt as finely tuned 
and welloiled as people would believe 
